_sText: Gg_Training_Ground v1.0 ----------------------------- Dominate the building or fail trying. This close combat map welcomes fast paced action and gives various strategic paths to flank the enemy. 40 spawn points and buyzones are featured in this map. This was a map I made a while back but forgot about it. After finding it in the depths of my "sourcesdk content" folder I decided to touch it up and release it. -Updated- Fixed the spawn points.
